## Lesson 2.1 — Python for ML
1. Topics:

+ Python basics (loops, functions, lists)

+ Classes & OOP for model building

+ Plotting with matplotlib

2. Exercises:

+ Write a class “SimpleDataset”

+ Plot a simple sine wave

## Lesson 2.2 — NumPy Essentials
1. Topics:

+ Vectorized operations

+ Broadcasting

+ Random number generation

2. Exercises:

+ Implement a matrix multiplication function

+ Implement a simple forward pass: y = Wx + b

## Lesson 2.3 — PyTorch Basics
1. Topics:

+ Tensors

+ Autograd

+ Optimizers (SGD, Adam)

+ Simple training loops

2. Exercises:

+ Build a linear regression model

+ Build a 2-layer neural network

+ Train it on synthetic data

3. Mini Project:

+ Train a classifier on a tiny dataset:

  + 2D points

  + Two classes

  + Visualize the decision boundary
